>>> STATUS: PROPOSED / NOT YET IN EFFECT <<<
This dataset compiles the raag and swar (sur) notation work of
Bhai Jaspal Singh Ji. The license below is a PROPOSAL for review and is NOT
finalized. It requires the explicit blessing of Bhai Jaspal Singh Ji's family
before this dataset is published as canonical. Until then, treat this repository
as a draft shared for review only.

SUMMARY (not a substitute for the legal text):
You are free to share and adapt this material for NON-COMMERCIAL purposes,
provided you give appropriate attribution to Bhai Jaspal Singh Ji.

  - Attribution (BY): credit Bhai Jaspal Singh Ji and this dataset.
  - NonCommercial (NC): not for commercial use.

Full legal text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/legalcode
Human-readable summary: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

SCOPE: This license covers the NOTATION, RAAG DATA, and COMPILATION — the
scholarly and musical work. The Gurbani text (shabads) itself is in the public
domain and is not claimed by this license.

Alternative under consideration: CC BY-SA 4.0 (permits commercial use but forces
derivatives to remain open). The choice between BY-NC and BY-SA is the family's
to make. See README.md and SCHEMA.md.
